{"id": 2138, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X腾讯青年营】在2028年，你希望科技发展帮你搞定哪些事情？", "description": "就是在等待这种直击人心的精彩瞬间。", "record_count": 8101, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201801241915131nJ26X5e8GLWTqEK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 261889, "content": "可以让人们的幸福指数上升吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209758}, {"id": 262146, "content": "我希望科技可以是拉近人与人距离", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247519}, {"id": 262402, "content": "希望人工智能统治世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148530}, {"id": 263941, "content": "希望孕育下一代可以靠科技解决，而不是女子的十月怀胎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256599}, {"id": 261894, "content": "希望科技能让家人健康，不吵架", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246600}, {"id": 262664, "content": "\n男神只要出现在公共场合都可以用手机看到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245893}, {"id": 261896, "content": "把我眼睛变好，跪求", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192764}, {"id": 262409, "content": "希望人类能团结点，人类太自大，要敬畏自然", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249317}, {"id": 261898, "content": "希望能解决单身问题，我是指机器人伴侣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 94667}, {"id": 263948, "content": "希望能来个性爱美女机器人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251547}, {"id": 262158, "content": "心灵平静", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916989}, {"id": 262414, "content": "旅行背包能装下更多更多更多东西还不影响旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172312}, {"id": 262160, "content": "把癌症和艾滋病根除", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 873028}, {"id": 262165, "content": "空中出行方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 472074}, {"id": 262421, "content": "脱贫暴富吧哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248482}, {"id": 262166, "content": "生孩子这事儿不要那么疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246000}, {"id": 262167, "content": "消除癌症", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247675}, {"id": 262425, "content": "医学界有更好的进步，治疗疾病更高效。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246085}, {"id": 261913, "content": "希望能有一个做饭机器人！每天想吃啥往里一输入～到饭点就做好了～", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246685}, {"id": 262170, "content": "城市交通更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221241}, {"id": 262171, "content": "延长我生命的长度或者宽度。\n100年不够活啊，那么多好看的书和电影，好听的音乐。我这辈子恐怕体验不完了(●ˇOˇ●)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089909}, {"id": 262428, "content": "学开飞机变得很普遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249418}, {"id": 263452, "content": "希望有安乐死。让人死的不要太痛苦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253573}, {"id": 262173, "content": "希望能帮我换个电子眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244816}, {"id": 261919, "content": "手机防盗功能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155928}, {"id": 267552, "content": "他还在连.任", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487377}, {"id": 261920, "content": "模拟自由生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246698}, {"id": 262945, "content": "cure cancer. ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251583}, {"id": 261921, "content": "黑镜这一季有一集讲到爱情配对的那种技术就挺好的，在虚拟世界里的两个人经历无数次重复测试，分开又再次相遇，再逃离，打破虚拟世界的围城，终于在现实里相视一笑。", "image": "img/option/option/20180125221239ipUZY9N8fQyjra1g.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246697}, {"id": 262182, "content": "我希望手机上的人工智能能帮我做更多的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103848}, {"id": 261927, "content": "希望科技能解决疾病给人类带来的痛苦 疾病如不能消除但可以没有痛苦的人性科技", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246732}, {"id": 267048, "content": "干什么都不需要钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270458}, {"id": 261928, "content": "能用在每个人身上就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 261929, "content": "一夜暴富", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195855}, {"id": 261930, "content": "希望能帮助父母的身体健康", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195855}, {"id": 262189, "content": "基因遗传。希望上一代的疾病基因不要遗传给下一代。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 862626}, {"id": 262445, "content": "恢复身体最佳状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249137}, {"id": 265261, "content": "能吧绝症搞定", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262540}, {"id": 261936, "content": "希望有无副作用的减肥药???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242864}, {"id": 261937, "content": "无限流量，手机电池可以用一个星期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233271}, {"id": 262194, "content": "ai可以去野外捡垃圾吗,把人类垃圾销毁", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868051}, {"id": 262962, "content": "我希望中国能将代孕合法化", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948020}, {"id": 261938, "content": "电器都不必插线了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233271}, {"id": 268339, "content": "那个。。。。女朋友。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423636}, {"id": 261940, "content": "交通工具都是天上飞的"